Package ru.nsu.fit.smolyakov.snakegame.model.snake

Class SnakeBody

java.lang.Object
ru.nsu.fit.smolyakov.snakegame.model.snake.SnakeBody
public class SnakeBody extends Object
Represents a snake body that consists of a head and a tail. The former is a single point and the latter is a list of points.
